headline: Costco earnings, Fedspeak, existing home sales: What to Watch
summary: Market Domination Overtime host Josh Lipton previews several of the biggest stories to come tomorrow, Thursday, September 25, including corporate earnings results from companies like Costco Wholesale (COST), CarMax (KMX), and BlackBerry (BB); a wave of commentary from Federal Reserve officials; and US existing home sales data for August. To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Market Domination Overtime.
